WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.740
Korrelyatsiya koeffitsientlarini ko‘rib 
chiqishda ba’zi amaliy qoidalar mavjud.

00:00:04.740 --> 00:00:08.325
Biroq, bu maydonga kuchli 
bog‘liq bo‘lgan o‘lchov.

00:00:08.325 --> 00:00:10.272
Ijtimoiy fanlarda

00:00:10.272 --> 00:00:15.070
kuchli munosabatlarni topish juda qiyin 
bo‘lishi mumkin, chunki odamlar murakkabdir.

00:00:15.070 --> 00:00:17.640
Shunday qilib, korrelyatsiya koeffitsienti uchun chegaralar

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:20.640
bu soha uchun ancha farqli bo‘lishi mumkin,

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:23.530
biz topadigan muhitli uyushmalar aytganga qaraganda.

00:00:23.530 --> 00:00:26.995
Shunday qilib, yana bir bor, bu amaliy qoidadir.

00:00:26.995 --> 00:00:31.185
Agar korrelyatsiya koeffitsienti 1 dan 0,7 gacha bo‘lsa,

00:00:31.185 --> 00:00:34.260
yoki -1 va -0.7 o‘rasida bo‘lsa,

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:37.200
bu kuchli munosabatlar deb hisoblanadi.

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:40.380
Agar u 0.7 va 0.3 oralig‘ida bo‘lsa,

00:00:40.380 --> 00:00:42.680
yoki -0.7 va -0.3 oralig‘ida bo‘lsa,

00:00:42.680 --> 00:00:46.800
bu o‘rtacha munosabatlar deb hisoblanadi.

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.153
Agar korrelyatsiyaning mutlaq 
qiymati 0.3 dan kichik bo‘lsa,

00:00:49.153 --> 00:00:53.070
bu holda bu zaif munosabatlar 
deb hisoblanadi.

00:00:53.070 --> 00:00:59.345
Esingizda bo‘lsin, salbiy korrelyatsiya 
koeffitsienti zaif aloqani ko‘rsatmaydi.

00:00:59.345 --> 00:01:02.310
Bundan tashqari, plot ham

00:01:02.310 --> 00:01:06.190
ikki o‘zgaruvchilar o‘rtasidagi munosabatlarni 
yaxshiroq tushunishga yordam berishi mumkin.

00:01:06.190 --> 00:01:10.065
Biz Anscombe kvartetidan ikkita rasmni olaylik,

00:01:10.065 --> 00:01:14.985
ushbu ikki ma’lumotlar to‘plamlari bir xil 
korrelyatsiya koeffitsientiga ega ekanligiga e’tibor bering.

00:01:14.985 --> 00:01:18.000
Biroq, ularning ko‘rinishi juda boshqacha.

